Jimmy Grant
Homonym Number:
Word Class: noun
Sense Number:
Definition:an emigrant; thence immigrant.
Origin: [none]
Register:
Register 2:
Domain: [none]
Region: [none]
See: also Jimmy
Pronunciation:
Notes: (also spelt jimmy-grant) Morris 1867 (So P.); AC 1845; [refer to the Morris 1859, 1867 cits:]
